To help strengthen the voice of the European business community, EuroCham have operated in affiliation with a number of European National Business Associations based in Vietnam including:&#xd;
1) Belgium Luxembourg Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (BeluxCham)&#xd;
2) French Chamber of Commerce and Industry in Vietnam (CCIFV)&#xd;
3) Chamber of Commerce and Industry Portugal Vietnam (CCIPV)&#xd;
4) Central and Eastern European Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (CEEC)&#xd;
5) Dutch Business Association Vietnam (DBAV)&#xd;
6) German Business Association in Vietnam (GBA)&#xd;
7) Italian Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (ICHAM)&#xd;
8) Nordic Chamber of Commerce Vietnam (NordCham Vietnam)&#xd;
9) Spanish Business Group (SpainChamVN)
